text: Quaint little place. Not crowded. Well ventilated. Reasonably priced food too!

Waited over 30 min for the food. Got the fish and steak combo set, but the steak was completely inedible. It was so dry and chewy. So tough & small! The quality of the beef is terrible! I understand that it’s “Fish & chicks” for a reason, but if the steak is going to be that bad, perhaps suggest removing from the menu.

Waiting for around 20mins yet get my food. Went to check with cashier, kitchen mentioned didn’t receive my order. Where all customer behind me is already having their dishes. Long waiting for my order, fish n chips too greasy as well as fries. Overall portion is not big and price on high side.
Ordered their Signature Set A, chicken + fish cutlet. Their chicken cutlet was super crispy! Portion is huge!! Fried fish was not bad too! They also accept CDC vouchers.

Emceerichardstyle Mic Rating
🎤🎤🎤🎤🎤
After opening for so long, this is my maiden experience with Fish and Chicks. Definitely they have their secret sauce for success!
